{"tid":2441010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「陰毛論」其實哈里梅根兩公婆數皇室單野係咪局黎？","createTime":"2021-03-10T11:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T16:43:58.000Z","uid":385047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9b0456c39636679960fe2243ae1c2505fde268","tid":2441010,"uid":385047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啊拜登「當選」之後曾經發表過一個言論話『There&rsquo;s no president who&rsquo;s a King,there&rsquo;s no Congress that&rsquo;s House of Lords」明寸英國，激到英國人扎扎跳。<br />\n<br />\n哈里梅根兩公婆數皇室之後，英國反君主團體「共和派」忽然出名，social media followers倍數增長，&ldquo;Abolish The Monarchy&rdquo;個trend兩日依然增長緊，已經接近7萬5，好多media都報導呢個trend。<br />\n<br />\n加上民主黨不停用梅根呢件事攻擊共和黨即將投票個bill種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪夾埋，啊登目標係搞皇室？同成個英聯邦？<br />\n<br />\n咁多巧合好似預謀咁，成個plan出曬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊登段野link：<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6WuJ726lIwI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6WuJ726lIwI&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=bddd16b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6WuJ726lIwI</a>"},{"pid":"2b67d75c2b88de578e3e648be2713040046154cf","tid":2441010,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"你估好奇"},{"pid":"5c27673bbe349fc29f64c14d5ea991bf146a09a2","tid":2441010,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"英國對支那強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d5af2bfae88d6f858b962dacec5e1c6f7b8906","tid":2441010,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"今日旺角撞車 一定係想搞大獲<br />\n<br />\n影響國際對支共唔認bno既新聞<br />\n<br />\n一定係轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dff9f25f4e742925d48b1c95baa0b08c5a55d7","tid":2441010,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:16:00.000Z","msg"